      "date": "2013-05-05 20:44:47.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/5f7075da-b5be-11e2-9d08-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
